{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/d5788/bg_preview.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 49.89473684210526%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"webshop squiller fashion\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/dbb61/bg_preview.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/19bd1/bg_preview.png 163w,\n/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/d3bcb/bg_preview.png 325w,\n/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/dbb61/bg_preview.png 650w,\n/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/6b691/bg_preview.png 975w,\n/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/91670/bg_preview.png 1300w,\n/static/20fe68a34bad209a2b6524dc40a9bb20/d5788/bg_preview.png 1900w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Het eerste project van mijn 2de jaar was het maken van een webshop, met onderwerp naar keuze.\nWij hadden gekozen voor <em>High end fashion</em> webwinkel, met kleding van allemaal dure merken. </p>\n<p>Door de namen van alle teamleden te mengen kwamen we uit op: </p>\n<h2>Squiller Fashion!</h2>\n<iframe width=\"424\" height=\"238\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nf2ex320JJs\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<h2>Tech</h2>","frontmatter":{"title":"Hoe maak je een webshop?","date":"2017-09-23","category":"Projects"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/Hoe-bouw-je-een-webshop/"}}